  "long_description": "This mod implements a tool for shifting nodes as with the pistons from Mesecons. It uses the API of `mesecons_mvps`, meaning that it is quite compatible with other mods (the API is widely used.)\n\nTo push a node, left-click the face you want to push while wielding the shifter. To pull the node, right-click the face instead.\n\n(If you want to move nodes quicker, a good choice is [![ContentDB](https://content.luanti.org/packages/ApolloX/teleporter_tool/shields/title/)](https://content.luanti.org/packages/ApolloX/teleporter_tool/).)\n\nThe tool can be crafted when the right ingredients are available, i.e. in Minetest Game (with `mesecons_pistons`) or MineClone 2:\n\n```\nP\nPS\n S\n\nP = sticky piston\nS = stick\n```",
